pubspec.name: math_expressions
pubspec.description: A library for parsing and evaluating mathematical expressions, supporting real numbers, vectors, and basic interval arithmetic.
A math library supporting REAL, INTERVAL and VECTOR evaluations of arbitrary expressions.
